Then, Meiqing,

591
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:10,070
please arrange for the two ladies.

592
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:20,950
You two,

593
00:27:22,430 --> 00:27:23,230
follow me.

594
00:27:25,190 --> 00:27:25,950
Let's go.

595
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:35,640
In the end, it wasn't in vain to kneel.

596
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:42,430
I really underestimated you before.

597
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:43,950
You've got quite the clever mind.

598
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,520
You're staying in the yamen now.

599
00:27:59,110 --> 00:27:59,710
You two

600
00:27:59,710 --> 00:28:00,830
can live here for now.

601
00:28:01,070 --> 00:28:02,190
Who is it? Who is it?

602
00:28:02,190 --> 00:28:03,230
At this late hour,

603
00:28:03,230 --> 00:28:04,920
can't anyone sleep?

604
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:07,830
Mr. Chen.

605
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:11,830
Mr. Chen.

606
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,640
It's so late.

607
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,640
What

608
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,710
brings you here?

609
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,760
This is the county's midwife.

610
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:17,760
Ms. Sun,

611
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:19,160
please help these two ladies

612
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,040
settle in.

613
00:28:20,350 --> 00:28:21,280
Don't worry.

614
00:28:21,280 --> 00:28:22,710
I'll take care of it.

615
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,800
Take care, Mr. Chen.

616
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,070
You two are the courtesans

617
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:36,920
from Mingke House, right?

618
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:39,310
Thanks for your help, Ms. Sun.

619
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,310
This room

620
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:46,880
hasn't been lived in for a while.

621
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,160
You'll have to clean it up.

622
00:28:48,470 --> 00:28:50,000
Didn't Mr. Chen ask you

623
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:50,920
to help us clean up?

624
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:52,310
This isn't Mingke House.

625
00:28:52,430 --> 00:28:53,880
No one is here to serve you.

626
00:28:54,430 --> 00:28:55,920
It's not a big deal.

627
00:28:55,920 --> 00:28:57,280
What are you talking about?

628
00:28:57,280 --> 00:28:57,950
What?

629
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,400
Did I say something wrong?

630
00:28:59,590 --> 00:29:01,110
Thanks for the guidance.

631
00:29:02,230 --> 00:29:03,950
At least you have some sense.

632
00:29:10,190 --> 00:29:11,110
Let's go inside.

633
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,560
What a dump!

634
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:26,070
Is this fit for living?

635
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:27,800
It's okay.

636
00:29:28,190 --> 00:29:29,400
It's a bit messy,

637
00:29:29,470 --> 00:29:31,040
but we can clean it up.

638
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:33,160
You always said outside

639
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,830
was absolutely great.

640
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:35,950
So I decided

641
00:29:35,950 --> 00:29:37,280
to go out with you.

642
00:29:37,760 --> 00:29:38,430
If we have to live like this

643
00:29:38,430 --> 00:29:40,110
all the time,

644
00:29:40,110 --> 00:29:40,760
what

645
00:29:42,280 --> 00:29:43,590
will I do?

646
00:29:44,230 --> 00:29:46,000
We're just staying here temporarily.

647
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,760
Once we get the removal papers,

648
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,760
we can leave whenever we want.

649
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:05,710
Bug! Bug!

650
00:30:05,710 --> 00:30:06,400
What's wrong?

651
00:30:07,830 --> 00:30:09,160
This one must be dead.

652
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,430
You take a break.

653
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:25,430
I can handle it myself.

654
00:30:25,430 --> 00:30:26,760
We're supposed to live together.

655
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,950
Why should you do all the work alone?

656
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:40,710
You two, here.

657
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,190
Thanks!

658
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,470
You old hag.

659
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:47,310
Just let it go; don't argue with her.

660
00:30:50,280 --> 00:30:51,430
You're such a fool.

661
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:53,520
She's just trying to humiliate us.

662
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:56,350
Let her do what she wants.

663
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:57,830
If we don't take it to heart,

664
00:30:57,830 --> 00:30:59,310
she can't get to us.

665
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:02,560
Come on.

666
00:31:02,560 --> 00:31:03,680
Help me out here.

667
00:31:05,780 --> 00:31:07,820
[Linfen Yamen]

668
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,680
It's on fire!

669
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:15,040
Are you

670
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:16,000
cooking

671
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,430
or setting the place on fire?

672
00:31:17,560 --> 00:31:19,190
I was just

673
00:31:19,310 --> 00:31:20,520
cooking

674
00:31:20,520 --> 00:31:21,920
and accidentally fell asleep.

675
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,680
That's a lot of smoke!

676
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,400
Yeah, it is a bit smoky,

677
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:28,000
but it's not on fire.

678
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:29,920
What else can you do?

679
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:31,950
Don't get mad.

680
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:48,110
You must be

681
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,590
the pretty girls my brother mentioned.

682
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:51,830
Your brother?

683
00:31:52,760 --> 00:31:54,070
My brother is Captain Cai.

684
00:31:54,070 --> 00:31:55,350
I'm the cook at the yamen.

685
00:31:55,350 --> 00:31:56,310
They call me Baozi.

686
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:57,350
Baozi?

687
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:59,110
Is that your real name?

688
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,950
My last name is Cai, first name Baozi.

689
00:32:01,950 --> 00:32:02,950
Cai Baozi.

690
00:32:04,280 --> 00:32:05,470
So, do you have

691
00:32:05,470 --> 00:32:07,000
meat buns in this kitchen?

692
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:12,110
You two haven't eaten

693
00:32:12,110 --> 00:32:12,950
since last night, right?

694
00:32:14,470 --> 00:32:15,190
Just wait a moment.

695
00:32:24,590 --> 00:32:25,640
These are the pancakes I just made.

696
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,350
They're still warm.

697
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,160
Give them a try.

698
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:32,190
They might be a bit burnt,

699
00:32:32,190 --> 00:32:33,640
but just peel it off.

700
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:37,190
I'm starving right now.

701
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,190
Tasty?

702
00:32:46,470 --> 00:32:47,760
So good!

703
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,190
Mr. Chen.

704
00:33:02,520 --> 00:33:03,920
Where did you get that outfit?

705
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:05,110
I borrowed some old clothes

706
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:06,230
from Captain Cai.

707
00:33:06,430 --> 00:33:07,230
That's nonsense!

708
00:33:07,520 --> 00:33:08,430
How could he

709
00:33:08,430 --> 00:33:09,710
just give the official uniform to you?

710
00:33:10,230 --> 00:33:11,230
Don't blame him.

711
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:12,680
I thought

712
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:14,230
if I dressed as a woman

713
00:33:14,230 --> 00:33:15,920
and moved around the county yamen,

714
00:33:15,950 --> 00:33:17,400
there might be some gossip.

715
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:19,040
But this outfit isn't right.

716
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:20,230
I think it looks good.

717
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,040
It's also convenient for doing things.

718
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:25,710
Your Honor.

719
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:28,310
Why are you here so early?

720
00:33:29,350 --> 00:33:30,950
Our diligent county magistrate

721
00:33:30,950 --> 00:33:32,400
comes an hour early every day

722
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,520
to handle official business.

723
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:35,190
While others wake up with roosters,

724
00:33:35,190 --> 00:33:37,160
he's the one waking us up here.

725
00:33:40,230 --> 00:33:40,920
Is this how you

726
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,070
talk to your superior?

727
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:43,310
It's just because

728
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:44,470
you're my classmate.

729
00:33:46,560 --> 00:33:47,310
Meiqing,

730
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:48,640
find a fitting outfit

731
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:49,640
for Miss Luo.

732
00:33:51,430 --> 00:33:52,160
You really let her

733
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,230
stay here to work?

734
00:33:55,920 --> 00:33:56,800
I know.

735
00:33:56,950 --> 00:33:58,280
I'll find her one shortly.

736
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:02,160
Thanks, Your Honor.

737
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:05,000
I have something to tell you.

738
00:34:05,310 --> 00:34:06,110
Go ahead.

739
00:34:06,560 --> 00:34:08,430
Now that I've left Mingke House,

740
00:34:08,710 --> 00:34:10,670
I want to say goodbye to the past.

741
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:14,120
Please give me a new name, Your Honor.

742
00:34:16,950 --> 00:34:17,560
How about we drop

743
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:19,230
the "Xiang" from your name

744
00:34:19,670 --> 00:34:21,230
and call you Luo Shu?

745
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:25,600
Thank you, Your Honor.

746
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,430
Find a fitting outfit.

747
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:38,950
Is there anything else?

748
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,150
Mr. Chen,

749
00:34:41,710 --> 00:34:42,870
is there anything

750
00:34:42,870 --> 00:34:44,430
I can do here?

751
00:34:44,670 --> 00:34:46,230
I can handle tough jobs.

752
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:47,000
You're not

753
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:48,870
up to something again, are you?

754
00:34:50,470 --> 00:34:51,280
I admit

755
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:53,630
I did play a few tricks

756
00:34:53,870 --> 00:34:55,710
to break free from my low status.

757
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:56,950
But that was just self-preservation;

758
00:34:56,950 --> 00:34:58,150
I had no choice.

759
00:34:58,280 --> 00:35:00,520
From now on, I'll have no secrets,

760
00:35:01,430 --> 00:35:02,950
just to do my bit

761
00:35:02,950 --> 00:35:04,040
to repay the magistrate.

762
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:06,630
I'll believe you this once.

763
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:09,360
I do have something for you to do.

764
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:10,630
The list of detained prisoners

765
00:35:10,630 --> 00:35:11,760
and their files are still unorganized.

766
00:35:11,910 --> 00:35:12,870
It's not complicated,

767
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:13,600
but it does require attention.

768
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,430
Can you handle it?

769
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:16,800
If I make a single mistake,

770
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:17,910
I'm willing to be punished.

771
00:35:18,910 --> 00:35:19,950
Come get your clothes with me.

772
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:48,670
Someone!

773
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:50,910
Why are you arresting me?

774
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:52,870
What's the reason?

775
00:35:52,870 --> 00:35:53,950
What have I done wrong?

776
00:35:54,430 --> 00:35:56,080
You can't just throw me in jail

777
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:56,870
without questioning me.

778
00:35:56,910 --> 00:35:58,230
You're disrespecting the law!

779
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,870
Let me out!

780
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:01,800
Someone, let me...!

781
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:04,040
Young Master!

782
00:36:04,470 --> 00:36:05,910
I can't stop you from yelling,

783
00:36:05,910 --> 00:36:07,230
but at least drink some rice soup

784
00:36:07,230 --> 00:36:08,120
to soothe your throat.

785
00:36:12,600 --> 00:36:13,320
What is this?

786
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,360
It smells so earthy.

787
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:16,120
Hey, anyone there?

788
00:36:16,190 --> 00:36:18,320
Where are the prison guards?
The jailers?

789
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:19,710
Is everyone dead?

790
00:36:19,950 --> 00:36:21,320
Hurry up! Someone!

791
00:36:21,710 --> 00:36:23,040
I want to see the magistrate!

792
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:23,800
Hurry!

793
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:25,710
Someone!

794
00:36:26,670 --> 00:36:29,280
You're new here.

795
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,280
Yeah, I'm new.

796
00:36:33,910 --> 00:36:36,150
You're from Linfen too.

797
00:36:36,390 --> 00:36:37,120
That's right.

798
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:40,230
If you

799
00:36:40,470 --> 00:36:42,560
need anything from me,

800
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:43,710
just let me know.

801
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:45,630
Thanks!

802
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,800
How many prisoners are here?

803
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:48,950
Someone!

804
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:52,360
Let me out!

805
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:56,190
Let me out!

806
00:36:56,430 --> 00:36:59,150
All the registered prisoners are here.

807
00:36:59,470 --> 00:37:01,600
If you want to check anything,

808
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:02,670
just feel free.

809
00:37:03,910 --> 00:37:05,190
Thanks, Mr. Wei.

810
00:37:05,190 --> 00:37:06,190
No problem.

811
00:37:10,430 --> 00:37:11,120
You!

812
00:37:12,470 --> 00:37:13,280
Let me out!

813
00:37:14,630 --> 00:37:15,600
Go ahead and shout.

814
00:37:15,910 --> 00:37:17,600
No matter how much you say,

815
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:19,320
I'll still outbid you by one liang.

816
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,470
Five hundred and one liang!

817
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:21,950
You have

818
00:37:21,950 --> 00:37:22,870
no reason

819
00:37:22,870 --> 00:37:23,710
to arrest us.

820
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:25,390
It's not too late

821
00:37:25,390 --> 00:37:26,600
to let us go now.

822
00:37:27,150 --> 00:37:27,870
Whether it's reasonable or not

823
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:28,910
is not up to you.

824
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,760
It's not up to me.

825
00:37:31,390 --> 00:37:32,150
You get to decide?

826
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:35,150
Do you know who my dad is?

827
00:37:35,230 --> 00:37:36,120
You said it's not up to me.

828
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:45,080
Do you know who my dad is?

829
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:49,360
Who's your dad?

830
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,120
I don't know.

831
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:52,040
What a coincidence!

832
00:37:52,430 --> 00:37:54,040
I don't know who your dad is either.

833
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:54,630
You!

834
00:37:57,080 --> 00:37:58,760
Fine, it's okay if you don't know.

835
00:37:58,760 --> 00:37:59,710
Let me tell you.

836
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:02,230
I'm the little son

837
00:38:02,560 --> 00:38:05,520
of Governor Qi,

838
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:06,950
Qi Menglin.

839
00:38:09,040 --> 00:38:10,950
So you're Governor Qi's son?

840
00:38:10,950 --> 00:38:12,280
I'm so sorry!

841
00:38:12,430 --> 00:38:14,120
We really didn't recognize you.

842
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:14,760
How could we

843
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:15,950
lock you up in here?

844
00:38:17,600 --> 00:38:18,390
It's fine.

845
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:19,840
I won't hold a grudge.

846
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:20,560
Hurry up,

847
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:21,870
let us out.

848
00:38:23,910 --> 00:38:26,120
But I'm just a low-ranking guy.

849
00:38:26,120 --> 00:38:26,950
I can't decide.

850
00:38:27,470 --> 00:38:28,190
I never said

851
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,670
to just let me out right away.

852
00:38:29,670 --> 00:38:30,870
I won't make things difficult for you.

853
00:38:30,870 --> 00:38:32,600
Go find your magistrate.

854
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:35,390
Tell him to come here
and get me himself.

855
00:38:35,910 --> 00:38:36,710
Oh right,

856
00:38:37,150 --> 00:38:38,230
make sure to mention my name.

857
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:40,710
Got it! I'll remember.

858
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:47,000
With your high status,

859
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,710
you must not be used

860
00:38:48,710 --> 00:38:49,950
to this jail food.

861
00:38:51,390 --> 00:38:52,390
Is this even food?

862
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,360
I thought

863
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,840
you brought slop.

864
00:38:55,630 --> 00:38:56,760
It's our fault.

865
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:58,560
I'll go get you

866
00:38:58,560 --> 00:38:59,870
some good food.

867
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,520
I can't let you go hungry.

868
00:39:02,190 --> 00:39:02,840
You

869
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,320
have some good sense.

870
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:07,320
You've earned it.

871
00:39:07,870 --> 00:39:10,000
Get as much food as you can.

872
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:12,230
Whatever's left is yours.

873
00:39:16,430 --> 00:39:17,710
You're really generous.

874
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:19,080
Thanks for the reward!

875
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:20,040
No problem!

876
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:21,040
Wait a minute.

877
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:23,320
Uh,

878
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,320
bring back some meat.

879
00:39:27,190 --> 00:39:28,950
Don't worry; I'll get right on it.

880
00:39:28,950 --> 00:39:29,630
Go on.

881
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,670
Why aren't you
eating your rice porridge?

882
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:37,520
We'll have meat soon.

883
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:39,120
We'll have meat soon.

884
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,280
Money doesn't matter now?

885
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,430
Bro.

886
00:39:42,670 --> 00:39:44,000
Your dad is really the governor?

887
00:39:44,710 --> 00:39:46,000
Of course!

888
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:46,910
Absolutely!

889
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:49,710
Wait.

890
00:39:49,710 --> 00:39:50,710
What are you doing?

891
00:39:51,870 --> 00:39:52,840
Please, please!

892
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:53,870
Help me, help me!

893
00:39:53,870 --> 00:39:54,630
Wait.

894
00:39:54,710 --> 00:39:56,190
Why are you bowing?

895
00:39:56,600 --> 00:39:58,320
Help me check my case!

896
00:39:58,630 --> 00:39:59,600
I'm innocent!

897
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:00,560
I don't want to die!

898
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:01,670
Don't believe him.

899
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:02,800
Young Master,

900
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,800
people like this are desperate.

901
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:06,390
They don't blink

902
00:40:06,390 --> 00:40:07,630
when they do bad things.

903
00:40:07,910 --> 00:40:09,430
Now they want to live.

904
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,430
I'm not like them!

905
00:40:11,430 --> 00:40:12,870
I'm really innocent!

906
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:14,520
The former magistrate

907
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,080
framed me for murder.

908
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:17,360
Now there's a new magistrate,

909
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,470
but no one listens to me.

910
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:20,390
I'm really out of options here.

911
00:40:20,390 --> 00:40:21,800
Please, be a hero;

912
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:23,000
help me out!

913
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,520
I'm begging you, I'm begging you!

914
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:27,360
Be a hero.

915
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:29,910
Alright.

916
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:31,760
Tell me your story

917
00:40:31,950 --> 00:40:32,630
honestly.

918
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:34,670
Here's the thing:

919
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:35,600
just a few days ago,

920
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:36,800
I went to my friend's house

921
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:38,230
to deliver water,

922
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:39,710
and they suddenly grabbed me.

923
00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:41,120
He was fine when I went,

924
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:41,760
but the next day, he was dead.

925
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:43,040
I had nothing to do with it.

926
00:40:43,040 --> 00:40:43,710
Then the former magistrate....!

927
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:54,150
What a scoundrel!

928
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:54,910
Don't worry.

929
00:40:54,950 --> 00:40:55,910
Once I get out,

930
00:40:55,910 --> 00:40:57,230
I'll get you justice.

931
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:59,080
Thank you, thank you!

932
00:40:59,080 --> 00:40:59,840
Thanks!

933
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:03,190
Just in time, food's here!

934
00:41:03,190 --> 00:41:03,950
Let's eat together.

935
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,430
Sorry to keep you waiting.

936
00:41:07,910 --> 00:41:09,430
No worries, good food is worth the wait.

937
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:22,430
What do you mean?

938
00:41:23,710 --> 00:41:25,080
You don't need to thank me.

939
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:26,430
I'm helping you out.

940
00:41:26,630 --> 00:41:28,320
I don't want you
to get into more trouble.

941
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:29,710
You got arrested

942
00:41:29,710 --> 00:41:30,870
for upsetting the magistrate.

943
00:41:31,190 --> 00:41:32,360
If there's another charge,

944
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,840
like bribing me,

945
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,280
you might end up in here

946
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:37,040
for a few extra months.

947
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:38,230
You're playing me.

948
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,080
You dare use the governor's name

949
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:41,320
to swindle me.

950
00:41:41,670 --> 00:41:43,280
I'm just messing with you.

951
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:44,950
I've been pretty lenient.

952
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:45,950
You're something.

953
00:41:46,040 --> 00:41:47,360
I'll remember your face,

954
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:49,040
you sissy!

955
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:53,000
Who are you calling sissy?

956
00:41:58,150 --> 00:41:59,470
I'm talking about you. What's up?

957
00:42:00,670 --> 00:42:01,470
Really?

958
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:02,670
Guess you've never

959
00:42:02,670 --> 00:42:04,120
looked in the mirror.

960
00:42:06,560 --> 00:42:07,280
The Linfen yamen

961
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:08,320
is rotten to the core.

962
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,280
There's not a decent person in sight.

963
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:10,870
The magistrate is abducting women;

964
00:42:10,870 --> 00:42:12,520
the clerks are sly and crafty.

965
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:14,710
If you frame me, so be it.

966
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:15,950
But this man next door

967
00:42:15,950 --> 00:42:17,230
is almost framed to death.

968
00:42:17,230 --> 00:42:18,280
If he really dies unjustly,

969
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,520
may heaven strike you down.

970
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:20,870
Strike you down!

971
00:42:26,910 --> 00:42:28,120
You have grievances?

972
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,870
You're just a lowly clerk.

973
00:42:33,670 --> 00:42:35,040
What can you do about it?

974
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,230
What's your name?

975
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,080
Xu Luan.

976
00:43:08,200 --> 00:43:12,000
Who dances alone under the moon?

977
00:43:12,540 --> 00:43:16,120
Stubbornly breaking free from chains

978
00:43:16,570 --> 00:43:20,090
Who lives a life with clever plans?

979
00:43:20,380 --> 00:43:23,960
Chasing in the sound of hooves

980
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:27,960
A restless soul

981
00:43:28,890 --> 00:43:32,700
Breaking out of the cage and flying

982
00:43:33,120 --> 00:43:35,500
Listening to the wind, so mysterious

983
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:37,560
The moon shines on my troubles

984
00:43:37,560 --> 00:43:40,360
This journey matters because of you

985
00:43:41,480 --> 00:43:43,760
The judge of fate

986
00:43:43,760 --> 00:43:45,950
Can't change my resolve

987
00:43:45,950 --> 00:43:49,580
Even if the ink dries

988
00:43:50,120 --> 00:43:52,190
Heaven overlooks all

989
00:43:52,190 --> 00:43:54,300
Earth tallies the hours

990
00:43:54,300 --> 00:43:57,200
I long for you to be by my side

991
00:43:58,440 --> 00:44:00,490
Clearly missing you

992
00:44:00,490 --> 00:44:02,570
The past is all scattered

993
00:44:02,570 --> 00:44:07,450
You are my bright moon

994
00:44:16,830 --> 00:44:20,650
Who dances alone under the moon?

995
00:44:21,150 --> 00:44:24,860
Stubbornly breaking free from chains

996
00:44:25,200 --> 00:44:28,750
Who's drumming at the door?

997
00:44:28,990 --> 00:44:32,890
Waking the dust from dreams

998
00:44:33,560 --> 00:44:36,730
A restless soul

999
00:44:37,520 --> 00:44:41,260
Breaking out of the cage and flying

1000
00:44:41,550 --> 00:44:44,160
Hearing the wind, secrets unfold

1001
00:44:44,160 --> 00:44:46,220
The moon shines into my dreams

1002
00:44:46,220 --> 00:44:49,020
This journey is enough with you here

1003
00:44:50,220 --> 00:44:52,400
It's unrelated to fate's details

1004
00:44:52,400 --> 00:44:54,570
Just because I never gave up

1005
00:44:54,570 --> 00:44:58,190
Even with many thorns

1006
00:44:58,680 --> 00:45:00,830
The heavens won't let me down

1007
00:45:00,830 --> 00:45:02,910
The earth helps me seek

1008
00:45:02,910 --> 00:45:05,690
Eventually, the clouds will clear

1009
00:45:06,940 --> 00:45:09,070
In this gentle and simple world

1010
00:45:09,130 --> 00:45:11,160
Laugh through partings and reunions

1011
00:45:11,160 --> 00:45:17,950
My heart only follows the moon
